- **`D3DRS_CLIPPING = TRUE`**: only at `install()` / `restoreDevice()` — never toggled elsewhere in the plugin.
- **`D3DRS_CLIPPLANEENABLE = 0`**: no user clip planes.
- **`D3DRS_LASTPIXEL = TRUE`**: top-left pixel fill rule — unrelated to near-plane.
- **`D3DRS_SCISSORTESTENABLE = FALSE`**: scissor off by default.

